The '''Agência Nacional de Inovação''' (National Innovation Agency) is a [[Portugal|Portuguese]] government agency funded by the Ministry of Science, Technology and Higher Education and the Ministry of the Economy and Innovation. The agency tries to promote [[innovation]] and [[Technological change|technological development]] and to facilitate cooperation between [[research]] and [[industry]].
==See also== * [[Science and technology in Portugal]]
