The '''Keeper of the Royal Archives''' is responsible for the papers held in the [[Royal Archives]], and is accountable to [[Monarchy of the United Kingdom|The Queen]].

Since 1945, the office of Keeper of the Royal Archives in the [[Royal Household]] of the [[Monarch|Sovereign]] of the [[United Kingdom]] has been held concurrently with that of [[Private Secretary to the Sovereign]].

